Title: BANCA
Body: Per community's request, we have re-made the technical video introdution for CoinUltra. We have improved audio quality. We have cut the length of the video so that it will stick more to the usage of the product. Hope everyone will enjoy this one!  The link to the Youtube video is below:  https://youtu.be/ah97ua0kRoA  Over the last week, Banca has officially announced her second utility for Banca token. The utility is named CoinUltra and it is already under development. It aims to focus more on shorter term sentiment traders and will use AI in the form of Natural Language Processing to automatically tag real-time news feeds and at the same time automatically classify news topics so that the traders will instantly know which coins to trade and what the direction of the trade is.

Title: BANCA
Body: Busy first week after the token sale.  Banca Weekly Update 09.03.2018   1.       We have successfully listed our BANCA token on HitBTC. 2.       Banca team has started first ever car competition on HitBTC with the main prize Porsche 911. It is the first time HitBTC is doing such event, they have spread this news on their main HitBTC accounts and balance page, also promoting it on their twitter and blog. The trading competition is based on buying volume, not buy and sell, but by buying banca tokens.    3.       Banca added a new team member, a product designer called Melody. Melody used to be a senior lead product designer at Ctrip, publicly listed company. 4.      Besides CoinAI we are also working on the new decentralized crypto investment banking platform. The first version could be released even before May. Roadmap 2.0 will be announced by next week.  Make sure to join the Announcements channel here, https://t.me/BancaPublic, for weekly updates and all important announcements.

Author: Banca_Official
Title: BANCA
Body: BANCA     WEBSITE | TWITTER | TELEGRAM      Banca is a Cryptocurrency Community Platform based on AI and Big Data   As an intelligent, community-based cryptocurrency platform, Banca allows its members to access institutional class analytics and information services using digital tokens BANCA. The technical implementation of Banca is based on three main lines: blockchain technology, artificial intelligence and big data processing.  The Banca team has accumulated more than ten years of experience in big data analysis, which will become an important building block of Banca community service. With those technologies, the community will be more accurate in recommending relevant community experts for clients, provide more useful data and information for a specific client and ensure trustful transactions on the platform. If the team can further improve Banca's functions and keep the community services abreast with the most updated technologies in AI, the aforementioned procedures will continually evolve. Eventually, Banca shall run as an eco-system by itself.   Utilities of BANCA CoinAI | CoinUltra | More   As of today, Banca has already completed the development of CoinAI, ‚ÄòWorld‚Äôs Leading Quantitative Research Engine for Cryptocurrencies‚Äô, as the platform‚Äôs first application. This has already established an actual user case for Banca token. CoinAI now has thousands of active users and is available in both English and Korean language. You may find the link to CoinAI below.  https://www.banca.world/coinai/index.html   In the pipeline, Banca continues to develop more utilities. This includes CoinUltra, the second application of the platform, which uses intelligent web crawling, neural network and natural language processing technologies to provide intelligent information service for sentiment traders. After finishing CoinUltra, we will continue to develop more utilities for the platform.

Author: Banca_Official
Title: BANCA
Body: We would like to thank cordially all those people who have shown their support to BANCA so far.  Please kindly note that there are no more presale discussions in the group and the team is working hard with strategic partners and exchanges to ensure that BANCA token can get listed after the ICO.  Unfortunately, since everything is under non-disclosure agreements, we are not able to discuss anything yet about exchanges progress before an official announcement.  Due to the hard cap being low and having high demand, we want our loyal supporters to have access to getting BANCA tokens, thus we would happy if you could go to our website https://banca.world/ to subscribe with your email address and ETH address, so that we could whitelist your participation in advance.  The following criteria applies: -          Participant must be in this Telegram https://t.me/banca_official group as a member; -          Register an account on www.leekico.com to participate on the ICO day. (KYC applies) -          Participant must fill in the form on our website with their email address and ETH address to be whitelisted as qualified. (Please make sure ETH wallet address matches with provided LeekICO ETH wallet address for the ICO) -          Participant cannot be a citizen of USA or China.  The email confirmation would be sent to the white-listed participants 1 day before the ICO starts.
